        <h1 class="headline"><span>Trump claims he ‘never meant’ Mexico would directly pay for border wall despite repeatedly saying it</span></h1>
        
        <h2 class="sub-headline"><p>Mr Trump has repeatedly promised that Mexico would pay for the wall</p>
</h2>
        
        
        
        
          <div class="meta-wrap">
            <ul class="meta">
  
  
  <li class="author author-last ">
    
    <a href="/author/clark-mindock"
       title="Clark Mindock">Clark Mindock</a>
    
    <span class="location">
      New York
    </span>
    
    
    
    <span class="author-twitter">
      <a href="https://twitter.com/ClarkMindock"
         title="@ClarkMindock">@ClarkMindock</a>
    </span>
    
    
  </li>
  
  
  <li class="publish-date">
    <amp-timeago class="amp-timeago" layout="fixed-height" height="20" datetime="2019-01-11T01:46:10+00:00"
                 cutoff="604800" locale="en">
      Friday 11 January 2019 01:46
    </amp-timeago>
  </li>
